ExpSyntax.val: IF ({0,3}='04','INQUIRY PRODUCTION SEQ. PLAN SUMMARY VS ORDER PLAN',IF ({0,3}='17','INQUIRY ORDER PLAN SUMMARY VS PRODUCTION SEQ. PLAN',''))

SQL_STMT_U.val: Select PLN_CD, PLN_MY, PLN_RES, MTOCD, COL_CD, COLI_CD from PRD017 where PLN_CD = ':1' and PLN_MY >= ':2' and PLN_MY <= ':3' and substr(MTOCD,1,5) >= NVL(':4', ' ') and substr(MTOCD,1,5) <= NVL(':5', ' ') and substr(MTOCD,6,3) >= NVL(':6', ' ') and substr(MTOCD,6,3) <= NVL(':7', ' ') and substr(MTOCD,9,3) >= NVL(':8', ' ') and substr(MTOCD,9,3) <= NVL(':9', ' ') and COL_CD >= NVL(':10', ' ') and COL_CD <= NVL(':11', ' ') and COLI_CD >= NVL(':12', ' ') and COLI_CD <= NVL(':13', ' ')

Select P.PLN_CD, P.PLN_MY, P.PLN_DAT, P.PLN_RES, P.MTOCD, P.COL_CD, P.COLI_CD, P01.MTONAM, P01.EFM, P01.CTEGRY from :1 P, PRD001 P01 where P.PLN_CD = ':2' and P.PLN_MY = ':3' and substr(P.MTOCD,1,5) >= NVL(':4', ' ') and substr(P.MTOCD,1,5) <= NVL(':5', ' ') and substr(P.MTOCD,6,3) >= NVL(':6', ' ') and substr(P.MTOCD,6,3) <= NVL(':7', ' ') and substr(P.MTOCD,9,3) >= NVL(':8', ' ') and substr(P.MTOCD,9,3) <= NVL(':9', ' ') and P.COL_CD >= NVL(':10', ' ') and P.COL_CD <= NVL(':11', ' ') and P.COLI_CD >= NVL(':12', ' ') and P.COLI_CD <= NVL(':13', ' ') and P.MTOCD = P01.MTOCD (+) order by P01.CTEGRY, P.MTOCD, P.COL_CD, P.COLI_CD, P.PLN_DAT
